Description: Greetings and welcome, waifs, strays, stragglers, vagabonds, bo ho's, buskers, tramps, vamps and pirates, yes especially pirates! So m'hearties this is a FIVE DAY ONLY auction, part of our Christmas sales from the stable of afterlife acoustics. For consideration, we have here a 'nice' forty eight year old Eko from late 60's or very early 70's with the nice sci-fi 'bubble' headstock logo. Now, this is a STRICTLY PLAYERS ONLY GUITAR!! an early edition of this classic Italian guitar, a somewhat well weathered wayfarer, and has been put through her paces for sure. Converted to a six string guitar (can easily be changed back to a 12 string) so it has the nice wide neck of a 12 stringer to suit those of use with larger hands, this plays very well and the pickup is good and punchy. This thing has travelled the world and then some, now it is your turn and she's going for a second time around on the carousel?! So lets talk turkey... ∞ Lots of lines, checks, scratches, dings, marks, cracks(in varnish not wood) on front, back and sides, so this is no corner of the room statuette! ∞ Otherwise in original structurally good condition with a pickup fitted ∞ Action good, set at low around 2.5mm @12th fret, can be raised or lowered with the original adjustable saddle ∞ Professionally set up and maintained ∞ UK Made nickel wound light gauge strings fitted ∞ Frets in good condition as is board ∞ Body took some flack over time, has a weathered part relic look with plenty of wear commensurate with a played guitar of age. Great mojo and good tone That is what it is about with these old loves, this has plenty of Jap mojo and that classic well dried tone, a players guitar. No reserve, low start pro setup, slinky Eko!! Greatest of luck to ye sailers of the musical seas! Enjoy!! SHIPPING USA + INTERNATIONAL - NOT FREE please ask for real prices! UK - Included in price EU - Included in price Please look at our other gear, Cheers and (dare I say it) Merry Christmas!! Item for sale elsewhere, sale can end at any time at our discretion. If you want to secure this for xmas please search for us online to reserve.
